column5: hello all heading out tomorrow.chili is cooking and the packing is just about done.oh i remembered i still have go to the beer store well i guess i'm not as ready as i thought. report in when i get back cheers jamie
Lots of beer stores along the way Jamie! South River is the easiest access with brown pop and hard stuff across the highway from each other!
Visiblity up this way right now is close to zero on the highway..hope it settles out for you by morning.
Don't forget the paper towels and a radio/light for the ice hut.  Forgot to mention last time, Satellite TV, but no spanky channels, only religious ones    Have a good trip.
Just mind your tounge while your out there! I dont wanna hear "Jesus C**** that is a huge fish and it wont come up the hole!"  Because we all know there are those on the ice that are sensitive.  G.
